<p>
	A beautiful candle in a tin with the subtle scent of red velvet which has a delicious cocoa or chocolate aroma to it. The candle is hand crafted using aromatic Cardamon &amp; Bergamot pure essential oils that will burn for approximately 35 hours and is a lovely red colour decorated with lovely white hearts.</p>
<p>
	When in use place the candle tin on a heat resistant surface. Ensure the candle is kept away from any flammable materials and do not move the candle while alight or while the wax is molten. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Do not leave a burning candle unattended.</p>
